26 corporation's directors cannot readily be assembled because of some catastrophic event. An
27 emergency exists for purposes of subsection (b1) of this section if, because of some catastrophic
28 event, it is impracticable to convene a meeting of shareholders in accordance with this Chapter
29 or the bylaws or as specified in a notice previously given for the meeting."
