37 PART VIII. EFFECTIVE DATE AND AUTHORIZATION TO PRINT COMMENTS
38 SECTION 8.(a) The Revisor of Statutes shall cause to be printed, as annotations to
39 Chapter 55 of the published General Statutes, all relevant portions of the Official Comments to
40 the Model Business Corporation Act and all explanatory comments of the drafters of this act as
41 the Revisor may deem appropriate.
42 SECTION 8.(b) Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective as of October 1,
43 2025.
